parameters: \n<High-class Bar Reception>Welcome. You must be Rain-sama, correct?

\n<High-class Bar Reception>We have heard about your distinctive features.
Your beautiful blue hair and facial features, as
well as your stunning figure, are exactly as we
were told.

\n<High-class Bar Reception>(However, I never expected a woman to come to
the bar dressed like this... \.She looks like a
prostitute, maybe she can earn some money working
here...)

\n<High-class Bar Reception>Your awaited customer has prepared a dress for
you, so if it's not too much trouble, could you
please change your clothes?

\n<High-class Bar Reception>I think it would suit you very well, Rain-sama.
Please allow me to guide you to the changing room.
\n<High-class Bar Reception>Please enjoy yourself to the fullest.
\n<High-class Bar Reception>Oh, Rain-sama. Thank you for visiting us again.

\n<High-class Bar Reception>Of course. \. As I mentioned before, your blue
hair, facial features, and figure are incredibly
beautiful and wonderful. They have left a strong
impression on me.

\n<High-class Bar Reception> If it's alright with you, would you consider
working here as a cast member? \. Rain-san, I
believe you could earn a considerable amount.
\CE[79]\CE[83]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Eh... me? I'm not particularly in need of money...

\CE[79]\n<High-class Bar Receptionist>Please don't say that... Lately, the number of
customers here has been increasing significantly,
and we don't have enough cast members... If things
continue like this, the other cast members will
become exhausted...

\n<High-class Bar Receptionist>Moreover, it would be too negligent to let your
beauty go to waste. I would like you to
demonstrate your worth at our establishment.

\n<High-class Bar Reception>If it's convenient for Rain-san, even just a
little bit... how about it...?

\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>Well, if that's the case... I guess it's okay,
just a little bit... in this kind of
establishment, I can also satisfy men's desires...

\CE[77]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(And being praised for my beauty like that...
I can't say I feel bad about it...)

\CE[78]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(Maybe I should give it my best shot here, for
self- improvement...)

\CE[78]\CE[79]\CE[83]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Understo od. I may not be able to do much,
but I'll help out a little.

\n<High-class Bar Receptionist>No way! Thank you so much...! \. We will
definitely support you as well...!

\n<High-class Bar Receptionist>Well then, please change into your uniform right
away and come to the floor. \. Thank you in
advance.

\n<High-class Bar Reception>Please come again tomorrow, we look forward to

\n<High-class Bar Reception>Thanks to you, our sales have been increasing.

\n<High-class Bar Reception>Customers, please refrain from coming to the store

\n<High-class Bar Reception>Rain-san... isn't it a bit too revealing? \. There

doing it so suddenly is a bit...

\n<High-class Bar Reception>I'm sorry, but it's troublesome for you to enter
the floor without permission...
\n<High-class Bar Reception>Customers, the reception is over here.
\N<High-class Bar Staff B>I will guide you, Rain- sama.
\OC[6]\N<Buster>That dress suits you well. Well, have a seat.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>... So, being here means you're also a member
of the 'Dark Owls'! \.What are you planning by
luring me into a place like this!?

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Hey, don't raise your voice. The staff is getting
startled. Just sit down and calm down for a
moment.

\OC[6]\N<Buster>Or maybe you're going to cause a scene here just
to catch me? Even if you're a holy knight, causing
trouble in an adult social setting doesn't seem
like a good idea.

\OC[6]\N<Buster>And have you forgotten that I helped you in the
southeast dungeon? \. Shouldn't you be showing
some gratitude towards me?

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>You still have a way with words, huh... Fine, I'll
take a seat for now.

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Well, I actually want to enjoy the alcohol
elegantly, but I can sense a formidable aura from
you. Let's get straight to the point.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Well... I have so many things I want to ask, it
might become morning before we finish.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Why are you here, after I was introduced? Who
exactly are you and what are you plotting!?

\CE[94]\CE[79]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Hey hey, don't push me so hard like that. And how
many times do I have to say it? I'm not just going
to reveal my cards that easily, you know?

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>However, considering the possibility that this
might be a trap, I'll give you a little
information as a reward for having the courage to
accept this invitation.

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>First of all, you were investigating the
'underground' of this town, right? There's a
facility there that doesn't exist on the surface.
I'm affiliated with that place. So if there's
anyone snooping around in that area, they're
connected to me.

\CE[94]\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>... What is that facility? I heard that there
are people like thieves wandering underground.
Could it possibly be the hideout of the 'Dark
Owls'?

\CE[94]\CE[79]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Well? I don't know about that. It's a secret
underground club over there. It's something you'll
find in any decent town, a playground for some
shady folks.

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Not only the betting matches at the training
facility, but I'm also one of the people in charge
of 'that kind of thing'. I don't know about those
thieves called 'Dark Owls'.

\CE[94]\CE[79]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>... Then, what is that magic... the magic you
used on me during the match? \. How did you... use
something like that...

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Whoa there, I've already told you enough for free.
You're getting a little too carried away.

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>And besides... what you really want to know is
about the magical device that was destroyed in the
southeast dungeon, isn't it?

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Ah... I've seen something similar to that in the
underground club. \.You're the one who destroyed
it and has been snooping around, right?

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>It's a deal. If you want to know the location of
that device, you'll have to pay a fair price for
it.

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>By the way, the club is invitation-only. You can't
enter without my permission. Well, you probably
don't even know the location to begin with.
Hehe...

\CE[94]\CE[79]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Certainl y, what I'm looking for is that
magical device. \. Regardless of you or your
magic, I prioritize the destruction of that.

\OC[31]\N<Rain>However, I'll ask you this one thing. What is your
objective? Are you trying to deceive me or help
me... What exactly do you want?
\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>What's the big deal about that? \. Well, that's...
\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>My objective is to make you mine.

\CE[78]\CE[79]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>.........I don't understand the meaning. \.
What are you talking about...

\CE[79]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Literally speaking, yes? Rain, my objective is to
make you mine, my woman.

\OC[6]\N<Buster>I like strong women. When I saw you at the
training grounds, I was instantly drawn to you.
And when we fought in the match, I made up my
mind. I'm going to make you mine.

\CE[78]\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>If you're not joking, I can't help but be
exasperated. Deceiving people, with an unclear
identity. Do you really think I would develop
feelings for someone like that?

\CE[78]\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Hah, you really are a woman. Do you think I'm
trying to make you develop feelings for me? If I
say I'll make you mine, then I'll make you mine.

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Listen, even if you knew it was me who was here
beforehand, you had no choice but to come to this
place. No, you must have come.

\OC[6]\N<Buster>Didn't I say it? \. 'You rely on me yourself.'
That's how, unconsciously, you're dancing in the
palm of my hand.

\CE[94]\CE[79]\OC[6]\N<Buster>So, if you want to move forward from here, there's
no choice but to follow me.

\OC[6]\N<Buster>Listen, I'm going to the \C[17] basement room of
this shop. It's not a place that ordinary people
can enter, it's a special room.

\OC[6]\N<Buster>If you want to rely on me to get information, come
later. I'll tell you how to get to the club.
However, as compensation for the information, I'll
have \C[27]you let me fuck you\C[0].

\CE[94]\CE[78]\CE[83]\OC[6]\N<Buster>I won't threaten or force you. You will choose
your own path by your own will. Whether you come
or not is up to you.

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>However, just by being fucked by me, you might be
able to protect this town from danger. Hehe...

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Well then, to the basement room, \C[17]come down
those stairs over there.\C[0]

\CE[79]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(Jazz is with me...! It's unthinkable for Buster
to embrace me...)

\CE[78]\CE[79]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(But... it's true that it will take time to move
